--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
claude-scientific-skills
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Source: https://github.com/K-Dense-AI/claude-scientific-skills
License: MIT License
Copyright (c) 2025 K-Dense Inc.

Some skills in templates/skills/ were inspired by the structure and concepts
in claude-scientific-skills, an MIT-licensed collection of scientific skills
for Claude. Our implementations are independently written for ML/AI/CS research
workflows, but we acknowledge K-Dense Inc.'s work as an influence.

Skills with conceptual inspiration from claude-scientific-skills:
  - literature-review/
  - hypothesis-generation/
  - peer-review/
  - citation-manager/
  - data-analysis/
  - critical-analysis/
  - research-brainstorming/
  - grant-writing/

Skills original to idea-explorer:
  - paper-finder/
  - paper-writer/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
asta-paper-finder (Paper Finder)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Source: https://github.com/ChicagoHAI/asta-paper-finder
License: Apache License 2.0
Copyright (c) Allen Institute for AI

The services/paper-finder/ directory contains a modified copy of asta-paper-finder,
a paper-seeking agent that assists in locating academic papers according to
content-based and metadata criteria.

Modifications from original:
  - Made COHERE_API_KEY optional (returns no-op reranker when not set)
  - Configuration adjusted for integration with idea-explorer